{"analytics_identifier":"OT1087","base_path":"/government/organisations/veterans-uk","content_id":"33cf4faf-f09b-457d-b516-0704547e1f89","description":"We provide free support for veterans and their families, including a helpline, Veterans Welfare Service, Defence Transition Services and injury/bereavement compensation scheme payments. Veterans UK is part of the Ministry of Defence .","details":{"acronym":"","alternative_format_contact_email":"ddc-modinternet@mod.gov.uk","body":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>We provide free support for veterans and their families, including a helpline, Veterans Welfare Service, Defence Transition Services and injury/bereavement compensation scheme payments.</p>\n\n<p>Veterans UK is part of the <a class=\"brand__color\" href=\"/government/organisations/ministry-of-defence\">Ministry of Defence</a>.</p>\n</div>","brand":"ministry-of-defence","foi_exempt":false,"logo":{"crest":"mod","formatted_title":"Veterans UK"},"ordered_corporate_information_pages":[{"href":"/government/organisations/veterans-uk/about/complaints-procedure","title":"Complaints procedure"},{"href":"/government/organisations/veterans-uk/about/media-enquiries","title":"Media enquiries"},{"href":"/government/organisations/veterans-uk/about/statistics","title":"Statistics at Veterans UK"}],"ordered_featured_documents":[{"document_type":"News story","href":"/government/news/eligibility-for-care-at-ilford-park-polish-home-who-can-apply","image":{"alt_text":"Ilford Park Polish Home","high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/69d7a44f2ea7bc150a394b5a/s712_IPPH_Graphic_v2.jpg","medium_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/69d7a44f69de22b2bf86f6b1/s465_IPPH_Graphic_v2.jpg","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/69d7a44f47eb6fd98375fa27/IPPH_Graphic_v2.jpg"},"public_updated_at":"2026-04-07T09:00:00.000+01:00","summary":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>Ilford Park Polish Home in Devon is welcoming applications from eligible individuals.</p>\n</div>","title":"Eligibility for care at Ilford Park Polish Home: who can apply"},{"document_type":"News story","href":"/government/news/ilford-park-polish-home","image":{"alt_text":"Ilford Park Polish Home","high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/697b7ddcaacd0dc9777b4feb/s712_s960_IPPH3_resized.jpg","medium_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/697b7ddc043a4ade0f7b4fee/s465_s960_IPPH3_resized.jpg","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/697b7ddc2ff8d10a830d5d61/s960_IPPH3_resized.jpg"},"public_updated_at":"2026-01-29T14:09:00.000+00:00","summary":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>The MOD remains committed to honouring Churchill’s historic pledge with the Ilford Park Polish Home.</p>\n</div>","title":"Honouring Churchill's Promise as the 80th Anniversary Approaches"},{"document_type":"News story","href":"/government/news/digital-version-of-veteran-card-launched","image":{"alt_text":"","high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/68f229eef5d433238a14c746/s712_DigitalVeteranCard.png","medium_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/68f229eee8e4040c38a3d032/s465_DigitalVeteranCard.png","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/68f229ee06e6515f7914c76e/DigitalVeteranCard.png"},"public_updated_at":"2025-10-17T11:26:10.000+01:00","summary":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>Veterans can now apply for and download a secure digital version of the HM Armed Forces Veteran Card via the GOV.UK One Login app.</p>\n</div>","title":"Digital version of Veteran Card launched"},{"document_type":"News story","href":"/government/news/eight-british-soldiers-of-the-great-war-laid-to-rest-in-france","image":{"alt_text":"Eight British soldiers of the Great War laid to rest in France","high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/68b02900ce0a11bb78a4f134/s712_JCCC_8_Soldiers.png","medium_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing